<section class="technical">
  <h4>Technical Notes</h4>
  <ul>
    <li>Postgresql database seeded with Faker gem.</li>
    <li>Posts, comments, and likes processed through AJAX request.</li>
    <li>Utilizes flash notices from native Rails and AJAX.</li>
    <li>Emails delivered with Heroku Sendgrid.</li>
    <li>Image attachments with Paperclip gem, hosted on Amazon S3.</li>
    <li>User search handled through SQL query.</li>
    <li>Environmental variables imported through Figaro gem and secrets.</li>
    <li>SASS styling with Bootstrap components.</li>
  </ul>
</section>

